                "fallback": "social.skewed.de: Tiago Peixoto (@tiago@social.skewed.de)",
                "text": "The idea of writing extremely customized software using LLMs is a curious one.\n\nIt may seem like a liberating prospect at first, but it's actually another instance of cloud computing: i.e. your software stack is *written* by the cloud.\n\n<https:\/\/isene.org\/2026\/05\/Audience-of-One.html>",
                "title": "Tiago Peixoto (@tiago@social.skewed.de)",
                "title_link": "https:\/\/social.skewed.de\/@tiago\/116515533636835286",
                "service_name": "social.skewed.de"
            }
        ],
