                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "The really interesting question is the one about alternatives. The obvious one is \"not being able to\", i.e. use off-the-shelf tools like everybody else. A halfway-in-between alternative is to use the malleable infrastructures of the past, meaning Emacs, Smalltalk, etc. Or a modern incarnation such as "
